        &kp TAB   &kp Q     &kp W    &kp E    &kp R      &kp T  &none                                                                        &none &kp Y  &kp U  &kp I     &kp O    &kp P    &kp BSLH
        &mt LCTRL ESC   &kp A     &kp S    &kp D    &kp F      &kp G  &none     &kp LGUI  &kp LALT             &kp LGUI  &mo 2           &none &kp H  &kp J  &kp K     &kp L    &lt 3 SEMI &kp SQT
        &kp LSHFT &kp Z     &kp X    &kp C    &kp V      &kp B         &none    &none     &mo 1 &none &none &kp PG_UP &none     &none           &kp N  &kp M  &kp COMMA &kp DOT  &kp FSLH &kp RSHFT
